    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines the Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP) Client Update Protocol (LCUP).  The protocol is intended to allow an LDAP client to synchronize with the content of a directory information tree (DIT) stored by an LDAP server and to be notified about the changes to that content. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
